data.title: Michael Gray (Instagram Star) - Age, Family, Bio
data.meta_description: Michael Gray (Instagram Star): his birthday, what he did before fame, his family life, fun trivia facts, popularity rankings, and more.
data.text:
About

Photographer and Instagram star who is known for posing his unique lighting photography and landscape portraits to his over 320,000 Instagram followers. He is also known for being a videographer and uploads film clips to his Instagram as well.

Before Fame

He first began posting pictures of his photography to Instagram in June of 2013.

Trivia

He is known for hosting his own FFA editing competition where he allows people to edit his own photography as a competition.

Family Life

He was born and raised in London, England.
